node.title: nodelock
node._create_table_statement: CREATE TABLE `nodelock` ( `nodelock_id` int(11) NOT NULL AUTO_INCREMENT, `nodelock_user` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `nodelock_node` int(11) NOT NULL DEFAULT '0', `nodelock_reason` text COLLATE utf8_unicode_ci, `nodelock_time` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP, PRIMARY KEY (`nodelock_id`), KEY `nodelock_node_index` (`nodelock_node`) ) ENGINE=InnoDB DEFAULT CHARSET=utf8 COLLATE=utf8_unicode_ci
